{"id": "1191537383221497977", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 19, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "指正一个断章取义的地方，我所说的“以功代守”只限于描述我的3C自研卡组的打法思路，并没有任何“环境所迫”的意思。何况我的卡组是没有带奶妈，与盾的论述无关。我认为心壁和希翼能流行的根本原因还是其廉价的费用与高于标准性价比的效果。且，希翼刚好可以用来防御图鲁的大招伤害，而心壁刚好可以顶一轮群体毒的压力。所以“以功代守”与希翼心壁之间没有我主观认为的逻辑关系。", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:24:09.854000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:27:00.105000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["710710398311202816"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1191275526933987398", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1191538608738422895", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 19, "author_id": "710710398311202816", "author_name": "xuyu_666", "author_bot": false, "content": "是我有些冒進了，但我自己玩下來的理解就是盾角自己本身的技能盾有點不中用，反而裝備這種誰大招好裝誰，費用又低又有傷害", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:29:02.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["632653171642335272"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1191537383221497977", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1191539390372130826", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "710710398311202816", "author_name": "xuyu_666", "author_bot": false, "content": "而雙神王圖魯的後期運營太強，又要將在對方點名後留有後手，多c陣容又者快攻陣容是必須的", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:32:08.396000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1191539832049115207", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "710710398311202816", "author_name": "xuyu_666", "author_bot": false, "content": "而在點名完圖魯或朵兒遊戲並非結束，必須加點防禦來為後期運營做準備，這樣看來透過裝備來獲取防禦手段是不二方法", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:33:53.700000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1191540872639168562", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 19, "author_id": "710710398311202816", "author_name": "xuyu_666", "author_bot": false, "content": "若我斷章取義的行為導致你的不悅我對此抱歉", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T00:38:01.796000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["632653171642335272"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😇", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1191537383221497977", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
