{"id": "1191761834416558091", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "【V1.0.28】1月2日20:30(UTC+8) 更新：\n\n【相位對弈：朵爾】\n● 狂氣爆發「理性，真理與現實」的回復生命效果從 40 下調為 26。\n\n【相位對弈：戰鬥】\n● 修復了有「阻擋」狀態的情況下受到「中毒」時，獲得的「中毒」效果數值錯誤的問題。", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T15:16:03.189000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-02T15:20:46.336000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1191762791518965790", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "写完朵儿的改动我去睡了一觉，醒来就发现奶量被削了，可谓是光速打脸 😭 \n至少朵儿确实改动了，只是没有按照我设想的方案改动而已。继续观察朵儿之后的表现吧，我认为我的方案仍然有合理性和可取性 🤑 （嘴硬一波XD）", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T15:19:51.380000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
